articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents: This site is for information about Kane’s Free Data Science High School Bootcamp, to be held for four weeks in the summer of 2021.

articles.title: Schedule
articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
Here is the schedule for each of the four weeks.
Week 1 The first week will cover Visualization.
 
Week 2 The second week will cover Data.
